{"tid":733984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雲滙睇樓客：陳生話Full Paid 800萬買兩房畀契孫","createTime":"2018-07-08T08:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T14:31:49.000Z","uid":73915,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f4421dfb19abcde60e1cfb4e056fa6c76e58f6fa","tid":733984,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"新鴻基地產(00016)大埔雲滙第二期展銷廳繼續開放，排隊參觀人流依然眾多，其中不乏一家大細的家庭客及年輕人。 <br />\n<br />\n睇樓客陳生未睇示範單位已入票，揚言「買硬」，並打算Full Paid約800萬港元買兩房戶畀契孫。他的契女張小姐指正讀小學的兒子於大埔讀國際學校，不想兒子每日返學放學都要來回東涌及大埔，故沽出東涌樓再買新盤。 <br />\n<br />\n曾生與家人到場參觀，他稱自己早年已上車，覺得現時上車非常艱難，「以前幾萬首期已可上車，而家有100萬都好難」。他的家人覺得樓價「貴到痴線」，但因「小朋友長大，唔夠住」，所以想入市，笑言買愈大愈好，但要「有錢先得」，認為呎價1.7萬元「好貴」。 <br />\n<br />\n另不願上鏡的黃先生表示，如果下一代無家人幫是不可能買到樓。"},{"pid":"9ad9d5128da8a62f28646228fefbe4acfcdef598","tid":733984,"uid":8511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"契女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fc94925f7a6a0cce971a93f4028beb76d93401","tid":733984,"uid":29314,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"同契女生既仔，原來叫契孫？"},{"pid":"dcd08af7aa8eb09aaea3137471df5ee46e45a738","tid":733984,"uid":193380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:04:58.000Z","msg":"Sugar grandpa<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00283c09f6b5df470abb043cf472ebb371ffc499","tid":733984,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:07:50.000Z","msg":"契爺 我屎眼好緊架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flower